    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/c3addc91ae0af8135181a3b390ac5bdb.poster.avif?t=1724343989\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/c3addc91ae0af8135181a3b390ac5bdb.webm?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/c3addc91ae0af8135181a3b390ac5bdb.mp4?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Rubber Brawl is an inflated multiplayer Brawler Royale. Get ready for a chaotic 32-player battle of tires where every bend can be fatal. Keep rolling and bouncing among a swarm of other tires, make them fall and destroy them to be the last one standing!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/a1f32bef03626b9da3ad8bcf39379648.poster.avif?t=1724343989\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/a1f32bef03626b9da3ad8bcf39379648.webm?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/a1f32bef03626b9da3ad8bcf39379648.mp4?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Multiplayer Brawler royale:</strong> 32 players ready to fight in the arena. But in the end, there's only one winner. It’s time for an all-out brawl battle royale until only one is left standing. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/24a3f8ae50ccb1f86522d3655b285b9e.poster.avif?t=1724343989\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/24a3f8ae50ccb1f86522d3655b285b9e.webm?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/24a3f8ae50ccb1f86522d3655b285b9e.mp4?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Overcome the laws of physics:</strong> Rolling, bending, bouncing... your tire follows the laws of physics, but it's up to you to overcome them to make you unstoppable. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/539ebe0a57f047603f55e0a05fbb2cbb.poster.avif?t=1724343989\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/539ebe0a57f047603f55e0a05fbb2cbb.webm?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/539ebe0a57f047603f55e0a05fbb2cbb.mp4?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Easy to learn, hard to master:</strong> Learn to control your tire and improve your skill to gain speed boosts, perform the best aerial tricks and knock down your opponents before they see you. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/e5276434cff8e3b2ba8b741aca6a85e1.poster.avif?t=1724343989\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/e5276434cff8e3b2ba8b741aca6a85e1.webm?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1717330/extras/e5276434cff8e3b2ba8b741aca6a85e1.mp4?t=1724343989\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>What a ride:</strong> Roll around a cosmic dump and use the springboards to bounce into the other tires. But don't waste time, at the edge of the arena, a storm is brewing and its ring will gradually shrink around the battlefield.",
